dataset.title: A new species of the water mite genus Austraturus K. O. Viets, 1978 from Victoria, Australia (Acari: Aturidae: Notoaturinae)

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Pešić, Vladimir, Smit, Harry (2023): A new species of the water mite genus Austraturus K. O. Viets, 1978 from Victoria, Australia (Acari: Aturidae: Notoaturinae). Memoirs of Museum Victoria 82: 49-53, DOI: 10.24199/j.mmv.2023.82.02, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.24199/j.mmv.2023.82.02
